description:
The last piece of "Music poem series" is for TwilightSparkle, and for some reason it is also for the friendship of Mane6

i must say one thing..... I dislike Twilight being a alicorn....
but that doesn't mean i hate her,actually, it had inspire me an idea.... of this music
because we all know there's ones goes said " All good things must come to an end."
so as mane 6.....
it will be pretty sad, even i can not take it too, but we have to admit this thing will come one day, friends will leaving us for some reason , maybe you are graduate from school, or you or them are going to somewhere else ,it is very sad to see friends leaving 
but always remember
friends will end, but not friendship, friendship will lived forever, as long as you really care
they will always lived in your heart, and so did they
when you said goodbye, you will understand how precious friendship are

I wont said not to weep , because not all tears are evil.

this music piece title "Twilight memory" it is mean for TwilightSparkle, but also means the memory of this just like the twilight sun "So beautiful, but so sad it is comeing to an end" the music describe a vision,

TwilightSparkle who had become a princess coming with princess Celestia to the west port, the twilight sun is shining above the sea, and the great ship is going to take her for the brand new journey,but matbe she will never come back....
Mane 5 come to the port , and they smiling, crying ,for the last farewell for Twilight

Twilgiht give her book to Spike, 

"The last page, is for your all... the one and only..."

than...after a few seconds....she can help herself and hug all poines and cring a lot

and than she get on the ship, looking back for the last time,and smile 

 the ship staring the journey, under the sunlight, under the sounds of sea gulls, and under the farewell looking of Mane 5
The great ship passing, and finally fadding to the west

This idea is came from Movie "The lord of the rings:The return of the king" the most touching and heartbreaking scence "The grey heaven" when Fordo is tring to say goodbye,and for this is the end of "Music poem series" but friendship will always lived in our heart

hope you enjoy it,
and thank you

whatever you like it or not 

~Sean.M
